     Instructions

     Instruction Manual - This manual was updated as of December 2001.
     (344 pages) 1,374 KB (Manual is in PDF format.) (01/16/2002)

     Questions and Answers

     TFR Questions and Answers - TFR Questions and Answers are published
     quarterly in the Financial Reporting Bulletin. At this site the Q&As
     are listed by issue number followed by the full text. A subject or
     TFR line number may be searched by choosing the Edit Find command or
     by typing control f. If you have a question that you would like to
     appear in this site or to which you would like an e-mail response,
     please submit it to tfr.instructions@ots.treas.gov. (09/24/01)

     TFR Training

     The Financial Reporting Division periodically conducts training
     sessions for TFR report preparers. This training is a basic course
     and is intended for individuals who are directly responsible for
     preparing the TFR. It is a nine-hour course, presented over two
     days. Information on future TFR training will be published as it
     becomes available in the Financial Reporting Bulletin.


